Removed a lot of packages that were unlikely to get used (RIP MudBun) also rest in peace Raymarcher, Boing Kit, LiveWatch (this one wasn't much of a loss), and Raymarcher. I did add a whole bunch of materials and started to add other buildings and env art though. Also updated a few behavior tree and entity packages.
Wrote up a little Time of Day and Celestial Body Module as part of the environment suite (and a test of the singleetons). It went exceedingly pooly but kinda got there eventually.
Updated AI pathfinding and behavior tree packs.

Added a bunch of new content from Kitbash3D and organized it by, roughly, object/material type. The naming scheme isn't my favorite but it's consistent so there's that. We may need to bring a few of the meshes into Toolbag or Substance for additional texture data generation but that's future us's problem.

Cleanup pass on SceneTerrainTest2 (also added other mechs. Project sanitization pass based on the Project Auditor that involved a whole lot of blind trust in a button called QUICK FIX. Attempted to try to import a texture set from Quixel Bridge.
Refreshed some of the HDRP materials that like to keep breaking and removed some URP ones.
